Author: butt___face
Text: Also, there’s absolutely nothing wrong with writing it down beforehand in case you can’t figure out how to make words once you’re in the office.

Author: jobbluetooth
Text: what I did was I told my therapist I was “having a hard time eating” and she asked me to explain myself and I basically just ranted about what I was doing to myself for ten minutes. you just gotta lay it all out for them
